185
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:10,480
It's not me,...

186
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:13,680
...it's fate.

187
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,160
It should not be like this.

188
00:27:26,480 --> 00:27:27,680
Then how should it be?

189
00:27:31,040 --> 00:27:34,360
I thought you will understand after going through all these.

190
00:27:43,320 --> 00:27:45,840
Did you design the Bagua Zhen to disable my Golden Eyes?

191
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:49,280
You still manage to enter.

192
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:55,600
You really didn't use the Golden Eyes.

193
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:01,520
Go in.

194
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:03,720
Go in and have a look.

195
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:08,400
Maybe there will an answer that you want inside.

196
00:28:58,560 --> 00:29:00,680
