201
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:07,600
This should be a man.

202
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:20,520
When Grandfather Zhuang joined the archaeological team,...

203
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:23,560
...he broke his leg from a fall and there was reinforced steel.

204
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:39,080
However,these 2 bodies are perfect with no broken bones.

205
00:30:39,760 --> 00:30:42,400
So he should have escaped safely.

206
00:30:43,280 --> 00:30:46,480
Xiaoyun, look at this body's teeth.

207
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:26,200
Their teeth are sharp...

208
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:29,320
...and have smaller gaps.

209
00:31:30,120 --> 00:31:31,080
It seems that...

210
00:31:32,040 --> 00:31:33,720
...the enamel damage is not obvious.

211
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:35,920
It should be around 30 years old.

212
00:31:36,760 --> 00:31:40,560
It should be a member of grandfather's archaeological team.

213
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:14,520
This body..... -What is wrong with this body?

214
00:32:16,800 --> 00:32:18,560
This body is a bit unusual.

215
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:24,040
The gaps between teeth are huge...

216
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,600
...and the crown is small.

217
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:29,720
However, the teeth root is exposed.

218
00:32:31,320 --> 00:32:34,560
This is obviously the teeth of an old person.

219
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:38,120
Old person? How old was he?

220
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:41,920
From the teeth condition,...

221
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:44,400
...he should be more than 100 years old.

222
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:46,120
100 years old?

223
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:49,080
The rumour of Feng Quan living until 120 years old is true.

224
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:50,920
It should be.

225
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,800
Unknown three words and the word 'for'.

226
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:11,960
Light?

227
00:33:13,920 --> 00:33:15,320
The extreme darkness will be the light.

228
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:18,080
The extreme darkness will be the light.

229
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:20,080
What does this sentence mean?

230
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:22,200
Don't bother about its meaning.

231
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,840
This is the coffin from Qin dynasty.

232
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:28,320
There is an eye. This must be the tomb of Feng Quan.

233
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:33,520
Xiaorui,after all hardships, we finally found Feng Quan's Tomb.

234
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:45,880
Male. Name,Tai Mu.

235
00:33:46,520 --> 00:33:48,840
Born in Qin Shihuang's first year of reign.

236
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:51,440
Died in sixth year of Zhongyuan.

