242
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:14,040
Xiaorui,you will not die.

243
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:17,360
Feng Quan lived until 102 years old. You will,too.

244
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:20,150
No. You can live until 110 years old.

245
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,440
120 years old!

246
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,960
I have said that you are blessed.

247
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:25,840
I'm still waiting for you to marry.

248
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:33,600
Why? Are you not happy for being able to live long?

249
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:43,190
For me,these aren't important.

250
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:46,150
I just hope that I...

251
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:47,630
...can be like all of you...

252
00:34:50,630 --> 00:34:52,120
...and leave here safely.

253
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:55,190
Xiaorui is right.

254
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:11,160
Report!

255
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:14,400
I'm Feng Quan, I have something to report!

256
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:18,240
Nonsense! It's the middle of the night. Speak!

257
00:36:18,640 --> 00:36:21,480
I didn't sleep and found signs of a quake.

258
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,960
The stars are aligned and there is a red light.

259
00:36:24,560 --> 00:36:26,720
There are unusual activities in the sky and the earth.

260
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,840
I think it is a bad sign.

261
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:32,120
