262
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:38,760
Don't be upset,general. He is a coward. It's his first watch.

263
00:36:39,240 --> 00:36:42,920
Please don't be upset,general.

264
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,520
You're scared as it's your first time,I'll not punish you.

265
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:45,280
Go away.

266
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:49,560
